Elana Meyer, OIS, (amụrụ na 10 Ọktoba 1966) bụ onye na-agba ọsọ ogologo oge nke South Africa nke meriri ọlaọcha na 1992 Summer Olympics na ihe omume mita 10,000.
Meyer setịpụrụ okporo ụzọ kilomita 15 na-agba ọsọ nke Afrịka nke nkeji 46:57 na Nọvemba 1991 na Cape Town
Mestawet Tufa ruru ihe ndekọ ahụ n'afọ 2008. Tirunesh Dibaba meriri ihe ndekọ ahụ na 2009, onye weputara ihe ndekọ ụwa ọhụrụ nke nkeji 46.28.
Meyer jikwa ọkara marathon Africa record (1:06:44 awa), setịpụrụ na Jenụwarị 1999 na Tokyo
Mary Keitany nke Kenya mebiri ihe ndekọ ahụ na 2009 IAAF World Half Marathon Championships site na ịgba ọsọ n'ime awa 1:06:36.
Ọ bụ onye nwetara ihe nrite ọla edo na 1994 IAAF World Half Marathon Championships ma setịpụ ihe ndekọ ụwa na ihe omume ahụ na 1991, 1997, 1998, na 1999
O nwekwara ọtụtụ ọkwa dị mma na asọmpi marathon dị elu.
